Package services

package services
The services package contains classes that provide various services and functionalities for the SC2002_CAMs application. These services include operations related to data management, user interactions, and other application-specific functionalities.
Since:
1.0
Version:
1.0

  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    AuthService
    The AuthService class provides authentication services for the CAMs application.
    CampDataService
    The CampDataService class provides data import and export services for the camps in the CAMs application.
    ChangePasswordService
    The ChangePasswordService class provides functionality to change the password for the currently logged-in user.
    CommitteeDataService
    The CommitteeDataService class provides methods for exporting and importing data related to committee members.
    CommitteeGenerateReportService
    The CommitteeGenerateReportService class provides methods for exporting reports related to committee members.
    CommitteeReplyEnquiryService
    The CommitteeReplyEnquiryService class provides methods for committee members to reply to enquiries in the context of a specific camp.
    CommitteeSuggestionService
    The CommitteeSuggestionService class provides methods for committee members to manage suggestions in the context of a specific camp.
    StaffApproveSuggestionService
    The StaffApproveSuggestionService class provides methods for staff members to approve suggestions related to camps they are responsible for.
    StaffCampService
    The StaffCampService class provides methods for staff members to manage camps they are responsible for.
    StaffDataService
    The StaffDataService class provides methods for exporting staff data to a file and importing staff data from a file.
    StaffGenerateReportService
    The StaffGenerateReportService class provides methods for staff members to generate reports related to camps they are responsible for.
    StaffReplyEnquiryService
    The StaffReplyEnquiryService class provides methods for staff members to reply to enquiries related to camps they are responsible for.
    StudentAttendCampService
    The StudentAttendCampService class provides methods for students to register for and withdraw from camps.
    StudentDataService
    The StudentDataService class provides functionality to export and import student data to and from a CSV file, respectively.
    StudentEnquiryService
    The StudentEnquiryService class provides methods to create, delete, and edit enquiries for a student.
    ToggleVisibilityService
    The ToggleVisibilityService class provides functionality to toggle the visibility of camps created by the current staff member.
